scenes.title: [VR] The immodest JK I met on a matchmaking app was kind to me because she liked virgins. Amiri
scenes.synopsis: I graduated from university and got a job at a famous company, but I've always been a bit of a nerd, so I don't have many friends, and I don't even have a girlfriend because my age = no girlfriend. I don't go out even on my days off, so I've been saving up my money... Then I found a matching app on the internet that I heard about. I took the plunge and signed up, and was matched with a girl named Amiri. When I looked at her photo, she looked like a gal-type girl, which is not my favorite type of girl. And she's smelling like a J-joiner.... I thought, “Is this going to work? I'm going to be cheated.” I was thinking so, but we continued to exchange emails and decided to meet.... I was nervous and headed to the hotel.
